      "title": "Salt Horse Gift Card",
      "body": null,
      "excerpt": "<p style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Give the Gift of Salt Horse!</strong></p><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\">Looking for the great gift for someone who loves craft beer, delicious burgers, and good times? A Salt Horse gift card is the ideal way to treat friends and family at one of Edinburgh's favorite spots. Whether they're enjoying a refreshing juicy IPA, digging into one of our juicy burgers, or exploring our ever-evolving menu, a Salt Horse gift card has them covered.</p>",
